        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "MINI FIXED BLADE KNIFE: Mini pocket knife features a three inch partial tang blade, a short quillon and plastic handle; ideal to include with general outdoor, hunting, camping or hiking gear where piercing, cutting tasks and smaller detail work are involved",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "CLIP POINT BLADE: Features classic clip point design, where fixed blade leads to a thin and sharp tip; mini pocket knife fixed blade is made from reliable 440 stainless steel, designed to be rust and corrosion resistant with excellent edge retention",
