        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Compact yet durable, this 6.25 inch Mini Clip Point Fixed Blade Pocket Knife from ASR Outdoor is the perfect on the go companion for every day carry or outdoor excursions. Whether you're camping, hiking, hunting, or just need a dependable EDC gear knife, this mini fixed blade pocket knife delivers high performance in a compact form.<br/><br/>Mini pocket knife features a three inch partial tang blade, a short quillon and plastic handle. The pocket knife boasts a classic clip point design, where fixed blade leads to a thin and sharp tip. And, crafted from 440 stainless steel, the blade boasts excellent sharpness and corrosion resistance. The clip point design offers precision control and versatility, making it ideal for tasks like slicing, cutting, and piercing, even through tough materials.<br/><br/>Available in two handle colors, blue or brown, the ergonomically designed handle provides a secure grip, enhancing comfort during use, while the small size ensures it fits easily into your pocket or gear without weighing you down.<br/><br/>For convenience, the mini fixed blade knife comes with faux leather sheath with snap closure, to keep blade secure and out of harm’s way when not in use.<br/><br/> Weight: 0.06lbs<br/><br/>Blade Length: 3.0 inches<br/><br/>Full Length: 6.25 inches",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
